  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the study is basically aimed at comparing two techniques of herniotomy by comparing there
      recurrence rates
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      in this study, the principal investigator will operate upon patients aged between 2 years and
      12 years by two techniques. in technique called mitchell banks technique, inguinal canal will
      not be opened and in Fergusson gross technique, it will be opened
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
